

[preface]
== Preface by Simon M Mudd

Welcome to a series of tutorials about http://lsdtopotools.github.io/[LSDTopoTools], that serve both as a basis of a short course as well as practical excercises for a course at http://www.ed.ac.uk/geosciences[Edinburgh] called http://www.drps.ed.ac.uk/16-17/dpt/cxgegr10094.htm[Eroding Landscapes]. Hopefully by following these tutorials you will be able perform some simple analyses using LSDTopoTools and will be encouraged to explore its http://lsdtopotools.github.io/LSDTT_book/[full functionality].